sequenceDiagram
    participant Browser as User Browser
    participant Gateway as Platform Gateway<br/>(Envoy) 443/TCP
    participant KRBP as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP TLS
    participant Backend as Dashboard Backend<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant BFF as BFF Sidecar<br/>(e.g., gen-ai 8143/TCP)
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Upstream as Upstream Service<br/>(e.g., LlamaStack)

    rect rgb(240, 248, 255)
        Note over Browser,K8sAPI: Flow 1: Authenticated Dashboard Request
        Browser->>Gateway: GET /api/config<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.3<br/>Session Cookie
        Gateway->>KRBP: Forward<br/>HTTPS TLS (serving cert)<br/>Gateway-injected headers
        KRBP->>Backend: Forward<br/>HTTP (localhost)<br/>X-Forwarded-Access-Token<br/>X-Auth-Request-User<br/>X-Auth-Request-Groups
        Backend->>K8sAPI: GET /api/v1/configmaps<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+<br/>SA token or User token
        K8sAPI-->>Backend: ConfigMap data
        Backend-->>KRBP: JSON Response
        KRBP-->>Gateway: Response
        Gateway-->>Browser: Dashboard Config
    end

    rect rgb(240, 255, 240)
        Note over Browser,Upstream: Flow 2: Federated Module API Call (BFF)
        Browser->>Gateway: POST /api/v1/responses<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.3<br/>Session Cookie
        Gateway->>KRBP: Forward<br/>HTTPS TLS (serving cert)
        KRBP->>Backend: Forward<br/>HTTP (localhost)<br/>User identity headers
        Backend->>BFF: Proxy request<br/>HTTPS TLS (shared cert)<br/>x-forwarded-access-token
        BFF->>BFF: SubjectAccessReview check
        BFF->>Upstream: POST /inference<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+<br/>User JWT (Bearer)
        Upstream-->>BFF: Streaming response
        BFF-->>Backend: SSE stream
        Backend-->>KRBP: SSE stream
        KRBP-->>Gateway: SSE stream
        Gateway-->>Browser: Streamed LLM response
    end

    rect rgb(255, 248, 240)
        Note over Browser,K8sAPI: Flow 3: WebSocket Watch Stream
        Browser->>Gateway: GET /api/wss/k8s/*<br/>WSS TLS 1.3<br/>Upgrade: websocket
        Gateway->>KRBP: WebSocket Upgrade<br/>WSS TLS (serving cert)
        KRBP->>Backend: WS (localhost)<br/>OAuth token via subprotocol
        Backend->>Backend: Extract Bearer token<br/>from base64 subprotocol
        Backend->>K8sAPI: Watch request<br/>WSS TLS 1.2+<br/>User Bearer token
        K8sAPI-->>Backend: Watch events (streaming)
        Backend-->>KRBP: WS frames
        KRBP-->>Gateway: WSS frames
        Gateway-->>Browser: Resource watch updates
    end

    rect rgb(255, 240, 255)
        Note over BFF,BFF: Flow 4: Inter-BFF Communication
        Note right of BFF: Gen-AI BFF needs MaaS token
        BFF->>BFF: POST /api/v1/bff/maas/tokens<br/>HTTPS 8243/TCP TLS (shared cert)<br/>User token or kubeflow-userid
        BFF-->>BFF: Ephemeral API key
    end
